Package org.firmata4j.firmata.parser

Interface FirmataToken

public interface FirmataToken
This class contains set of constants that represent tokens of Firmata protocol.
In addition it contains headers and keys of events that occur when Firmata messages are received.
Author:
Oleg Kurbatov <o.v.kurbatov@gmail.com>

  • Field Details

    • FIRMATA_MAJOR_VERSION

      static final byte FIRMATA_MAJOR_VERSION
      Version numbers for the protocol. The protocol is still changing, so these version numbers are important. This number can be queried so that host software can test whether it will be compatible with the currently installed firmware.
